{"tid":1019344,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"旅日中國遊客無視飯店禁菸　被抓後辯「只有點火」","createTime":"2019-02-13T01:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T16:45:34.000Z","uid":187109,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4387fe0498ac0496248c567c375eb6534f7409f2","tid":1019344,"uid":187109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:04:03.000Z","msg":"中國遊客到日本旅遊，入住禁菸的飯店，無視櫃台人員的提醒，在自己房間內抽菸，被員工發現後還辯稱「只有點火沒有抽」。<br />\n據《news-postseven》報導，東京一處高級飯店全館禁菸，相當受帶小孩出遊家庭的歡迎。不過有中國觀光客一家入住，在櫃檯相關手續的時候，櫃台人員就看到中國遊客胸口口袋放有香菸，於是特別提醒飯店全面禁菸，並說明如果吸菸的話將另外收取清潔費，並出示同意書請中國遊客簽名。<br />\n<br />\n但到了晚上的時候，飯店人員在樓層巡邏，發現入住的這家中國遊客房間，聞到了香菸的味道，於是透過對講機，請該房的遊客開門，說明「因為是全館禁菸，所以請不要抽菸」，沒想到中國遊客辯稱「只有點火而以，沒有抽」，而且並沒有付飯店清潔費用。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190212/1516248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190212%2F1516248&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiTUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=de36f616\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190212%2F1516248&h=f45d92a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190212/1516248</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Dwm2aO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Dwm2aO.png&h=039e6305&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b235887efe068f5c96483576407586ce9a3df445","tid":1019344,"uid":187109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:07:07.000Z","msg":"中國又燃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af2aae5617d51b4a90808dec8496189fa128cb4","tid":1019344,"uid":37413,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:18:57.000Z","msg":"支國人嘅詭辯真係世界第一，永遠自己都無錯"},{"pid":"6ff2d98abb54cdabc1edc01568974533fdfa120f","tid":1019344,"uid":187109,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T01:22:32.000Z","msg":"支那狗成